{"tid":1559790,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【支共末日】今年首8個月中美貿易總額2.42萬億元　下降9%","createTime":"2019-09-11T03:16:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-11T03:35:40.000Z","uid":66087,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"ace8007260b821a8c1478cdba50cedca41a4884a","tid":1559790,"uid":66087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T03:16:02.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/china/article/2245230\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Finstantnews%2Fchina%2Farticle%2F2245230&d=3A5iQKMTOMHlOvaIjHeReiEyVFbloTKGHdwbQdNTMZo%3D&h=8d9011c4\" target=\"_blank\">https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/china/article/2245230</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/amenews/20181215/photo/bkn-20181215210107926-1215_00972_001_01p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Famenews%2F20181215%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20181215210107926-1215_00972_001_01p.jpg&h=7425081d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n2019年9月8日　財經<br />\n<br />\n今年前8個月，中國大陸貿易進出口總值20.13萬億元人民幣，比去年同期增長3.6%。其中，出口10.95萬億元，增長6.1%；進口9.18萬億元，增長0.8%；貿易順差1.77萬億元，擴大46%。<br />\n<br />\n歐盟為中國第一大貿易夥伴，中歐貿易總額3.15萬億元，增長9.7%。東盟為中國第二大貿易夥伴，與東盟貿易總額為2.74萬億元，增長11.7%。<br />\n<br />\n美國為中國第三大貿易夥伴，中美貿易總額為2.42萬億元，下降9%，佔外貿總值的12%。<strong>其中，對美國出口1.88萬億元，下降3.7%；自美國進口5450.1億元，下降23.5%，顯示兩國貿易磨擦升溫。</strong>"},{"pid":"6f5c424fb3365046f5f1a6a7bc93f208071b51b2","tid":1559790,"uid":10014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T03:18:37.000Z","msg":"仆街 好似出口無乜點跌既喂？"},{"pid":"f4226f41799c7c520463bc4f79637f3c4ac84b86","tid":1559790,"uid":163447,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6f5c424fb3365046f5f1a6a7bc93f208071b51b2","tid":1559790,"uid":10014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T03:18:37.000Z","msg":"仆街 好似出口無乜點跌既喂？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T03:26:00.000Z","msg":"蝕住做?"},{"pid":"c21c6679761b681873ad4f82f0af0591af271042","tid":1559790,"uid":271234